{"tid":2398802,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"雨琦拿自拍照追問「像不像太妍？」　被小娟「真心話」氣到躲廁所","createTime":"2021-02-07T15:04:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-07T19:47:55.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6e7281d001aee1b32253e3b31138b5c9362d8e5d","tid":2398802,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T15:04:04.000Z","msg":"南韓女團(G)I-DLE（(여자)아이들）在2018年出道，強烈的舞台表演以及具特色的曲風，使她們擁有超高人氣，私底下反轉的打鬧相處模式也圈了許多粉絲。近日，隊長小娟以及成員穗珍、雨琦一起登上了網路節目，小娟爆料曾因為不認同雨琦「長得像太妍」的說法，而與對方吵架，相愛相殺的畫面在粉絲間引起了熱烈討論。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5444/d5444529.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5444%2Fd5444529.jpg&h=c25713cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲小娟、穗珍、雨琦一起登上《FACE ID》。（圖／翻攝(G)I-DLE IG）<br />\n<br />\n小娟在網路節目《FACE ID》上，爆料跟雨琦過去吵架的事件，說道：「妳以前跟我因為這個吵架過，因為妳說妳像太妍前輩。」突如其來的發言讓雨琦不知所措並抓著她一陣大笑，直呼「等等！等一下！」，並且試圖想解釋，一旁穗珍則悠閒地喝著飲料，證實確實發生過這件事，附和小娟說「沒錯」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5444/5444530.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5444%2F5444530.jpg&h=d45132f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲小娟爆料雨琦曾拿自拍照抓著自己問「像不像太妍前輩」。（圖／翻攝YouTube／카카오TV）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5444/d5444541.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5444%2Fd5444541.jpg&h=62a871f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲少女時代隊長太妍。（圖／翻攝太妍IG）<br />\n<br />\n雨琦解釋是因為上學時，很多人都那樣講過，急忙說道：「我那時因為有瀏海，蠻漂亮的。」接著小娟加碼爆料，透露當時雨琦經常自拍完跑來問自己「像不像太妍前輩？」，她對此真摯地回答「沒有，一點都不像，妳很漂亮，但真的不像」，沒想到雨琦因此生氣跑進廁所。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5444/5444531.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5444%2F5444531.jpg&h=18fb3269&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲小娟認真回答「不像」。（圖／翻攝YouTube／카카오TV）<br />\n<br />\n穗珍還模仿起雨琦生氣的樣子，大力踏步離場，她當時走進廁所查看，看到雨琦很生氣地洗手，3人回憶起當時的場景都笑到不行，雨琦也表示自己當時真的很生氣，在廁所整整待了5分鐘，成員間的真實互動也讓網友笑翻。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5444/d5444532.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5444%2Fd5444532.jpg&h=88461bda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲穗珍模仿生氣的雨琦。（圖／翻攝YouTube／카카오TV）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5FjB5L6wZYw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D5FjB5L6wZYw&d=NdDBecmRZzhky7sLgKmJOf3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=bc94e6ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5FjB5L6wZYw</a>"},{"pid":"77826c9257c67e6e5866b89f216063bf4d042d28","tid":2398802,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T15:07:44.000Z","msg":"勁qq...<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccdedc18580aad60e072b4d0c3f0ddbd2ccb428c","tid":2398802,"uid":16659,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"77826c9257c67e6e5866b89f216063bf4d042d28","tid":2398802,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T15:07:44.000Z","msg":"勁qq...<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T15:10:17.000Z","msg":"Everyone qq 除了yq<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8301b5dace6128be8b791b340562ed1dc6b4cb3b","tid":2398802,"uid":5597,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T15:12:16.000Z","msg":"韓妹咁撚樣衰成日開po<br />\n韓妹垃圾睇既仲垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a00371e6f67f43b60f1d92c983f6cc93cbff913c","tid":2398802,"uid":255310,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T15:24:35.000Z","msg":"太妍正式啲"},{"pid":"39f675aeb11f4b87858e0f7d0b356499c30968ba","tid":2398802,"uid":43061,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8301b5dace6128be8b791b340562ed1dc6b4cb3b","tid":2398802,"uid":5597,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T15:12:16.000Z","msg":"韓妹咁撚樣衰成日開po<br />\n韓妹垃圾睇既仲垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T17:03:51.000Z","msg":"你見撚到韓妹topic都死入黎 咪一樣係垃圾啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66df99929e121d0e243e849a5b7de5004cc34f20","tid":2398802,"uid":382064,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T19:47:55.000Z","msg":"成對淨係唔鐘意yq<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}